title: Florida Gov. DeSantis says he has no plans for statewide stay-at-home order, despite warnings
description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis repeated Wednesday that a statewide stay-at-home order in Florida would be “inappropriate,” and he had no plans to enact such a policy.
